# OpsDeck Hero GIF

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 700
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Padding 20
Set CursorBlink false

# Setup PATH (hidden)
Hide
Type `export PATH=/Users/jason/Documents/GitHub/OpsDeck:$PATH && clear`
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show

# Daily brief — the killer feature
Type "opsdeck brief"
Enter
Sleep 6s

# Productivity metrics
Type "opsdeck metrics"
Enter
Sleep 5s
